    <h2>{`新建一个组件`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-shell"
      }}>{`npm run new
`}</code></pre>
    <h2>{`构建项目`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-shell"
      }}>{`npm run build
